    },
    {
      "text": "Engineers, moderators, and planners constantly watch for these patterns: algorithms that lock in tastes, moderators dampening viral harm, or traffic planners smoothing flows. Professionals spot and manage loops every day.",
      "title": "Professionals Spotting Loops"
    }
  ]
}

{
